  "description_html": "<p data-start=\"1000\" data-end=\"1021\"><strong>Team:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"1025\" data-end=\"1075\">Each team must register before the event begins.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1078\" data-end=\"1146\">Teams will choose or be assigned a side at the start of the event.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1149\" data-end=\"1195\">Once a side is chosen, it cannot be changed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1202\" data-end=\"1220\"><strong>Event:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"1224\" data-end=\"1294\">The event will unfold in multiple phases across the 4-hour duration.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1297\" data-end=\"1348\">Each phase reveals new developments in the story.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1351\" data-end=\"1424\">Progression depends on participation, observation, and decision-making.</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-start=\"1431\" data-end=\"1456\"><strong>Rules:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"1460\" data-end=\"1532\">Teams must pay close attention to all story segments and instructions.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1535\" data-end=\"1597\">Information provided at any point may become relevant later.</li>\n<li data-start=\"1600\" data-end=\"1677\">Decisions made by teams can influence their standing and available options.</li>\n</ul>",
